  "prompt": "Which are the top 5 Bollywood songs of 2015?",
  "response": "The top 5 Bollywood songs of 2015 can vary based on different sources and opinions. However, some widely popular and acclaimed songs from that year include:\n\n1. **Gerua** - From the movie \"Dilwale,\" sung by Arijit Singh and Antara Mitra.\n2. **Chittiyaan Kalaiyaan** - From the movie \"Roy,\" sung by Kanika Kapoor.\n3. **Bang Bang** - From the movie \"Bang Bang,\" sung by Benny Dayal and Neeti Mohan (Note: The movie was released in 2014, but the song remained popular in 2015).\n4. **Sooraj Dooba Hain** - From the movie \"Roy,\" sung by Arijit Singh and Aditi Singh Sharma.\n5. **Prem Ratan Dhan Payo** - From the movie \"Prem Ratan Dhan Payo,\" sung by Palak Muchhal.\n\nThese songs were among the most popular and received a lot of airplay and appreciation in 2015.",
